#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Admin" menu</h2>
For most users, the administration menu allows you to change:
<ul>
<li>Your name
<li>Your password
<li>Your e-mail address
<li>Your phone number
<li>Your fax number
<li>Your mailing address
</ul>
You can also enter any activation code sent to you which might
give you additional privileges.
<p>If you enter a new e-mail address, a new phone number, a new
fax number or a new mailing address, the system <em>may</em>
attempt to confirm that you are at those addresses by sending
messages to them with activation codes.
<p>After you have made your changes, press the Modify button.

